mil.emp3.api.interfaces

Interface IScreenCaptureCallback


  • public interface IScreenCaptureCallback
    This interface defines the screen capture callback methods. A call to IMap.getScreenCapture must provide an implementation of this interface. The methods defined are called to provide the outcome of the screen capture operation.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void captureFailed(java.lang.Exception Ex)
      This method is called when the screen capture fails.
      void captureSuccess(ICapture capture)
      This method is called when the screen capture has been performed and available in the capture object.
